quran[7{c,v,t}:
35,12,aur dono darya ( mil kar ) yaksaa nahi ho jatay. yeh to meetha hai pyaas bujhanay wala. jis ka pani Khushgawar hai aur yeh khaari hai karva. aur sab se tum taaza gosht khatay ho aur zewar nikaltay ho jisay pehantay ho. aur tum darya mein kashtiyon ko dekhte ho ke ( pani ko ) pharti chali aati hain taakay tum is ke fazl se ( muaash ) talaash karo aur taakay shukar karo
35,13,wohi raat ko din mein daakhil karta aur ( wohi ) din ko raat mein daakhil karta hai aur isi ne Sooraj aur chaand ko kaam mein laga diya hai. har aik aik waqt muqarrar taq chal raha hai. yahi khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai isi ki badshahi hai. aur jin logon ko tum is ke siwa pkarte ho woh khajoor ki ghuthli ke chilkay ke barabar bhi to ( kisi cheez ke ) maalik nahi
35,14,agar tum un ko poukaro to woh tumhari pukaar nah sunen aur agar sun bhi len to tumhari baat ko qubool nah kar saken. aur qayamat ke din tumahray shirk se inkaar kar dein ge. aur ( khuday-e ) bakhabar ki terhan tum ko koi khabar nahi day ga
35,15,logo tum ( sab ) khuda ke mohtaaj ho aur khuda be parwa sazawar ( hamd وثنا ) hai
35,16,agar chahay to tum ko nabood kardey aur nai makhloqaat laa abad kere
35,17,aur yeh khuda ko kuch mushkil nahi
35,18,aur koi uthany wala dosray ka boojh nah uthaye ga. aur koi boojh mein daba howa apna boojh btane ko kisi ko bulaye to koi is mein se kuch nah uthaye ga agarchay qaraabat daar hi ho. ( ae paighambar ) tum unhi logon ko nasiyaat kar saktay ho jo ban dekhe apne perwar-digaar se drtay aur namaz balaltzam parhte hain. aur jo shakhs pak hota hai apne hi liye pak hota hai. aur ( sab ko ) khuda hi ki taraf lout kar jana hai
